{"tid":1559720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《紐約時報》專欄作家稱台灣擬空襲福建　國防部駁：不實假消息","createTime":"2019-09-11T02:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T05:09:24.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ce17b4352d41cdedad084417c830c0b544d2d82b","tid":1559720,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:33:27.000Z","msg":"美國《紐約時報》專欄作家紀思道（Nicholas Donabet Kristof）近期發表題為「台灣可能是美中戰爭導火線」文章，內容指台灣外交部長吳釗燮曾證實，國軍正針對中國制定「防禦和進攻計畫」，且有高級官員提到，報復手段包括「空襲中國福建省」。不過國防部對此駁斥，不實假訊息。<br />\n<br />\n國防部說，國軍秉「防衛固守、重層嚇阻」之軍事戰略指導，以維護國土主權、自由民主，確保區域和平與台海穩定。此外，面對中共威脅，透過聯合情監偵，國軍能隨時掌握區域情勢及敵情動態，並保持高度警覺，適時應處，以支持防衛構想及確保國家安全。另藉各項戰演訓時機，持續強化國軍建軍備戰能力，國軍有信心有能力保衛國家安全，籲請國人安心。<br />\n<br />\n吳釗燮受訪則說，「國防部會針對不同的想定，制定我們的攻防計畫，確保國家安全。」（政治中心／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190910/1630958/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190910%2F1630958%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=18aed56e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190910%2F1630958%2F&h=84cf6f10\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190910/1630958/</a>"},{"pid":"97ceb538c306dd39a81aeb8b98b21c446e3103a8","tid":1559720,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:34:42.000Z","msg":"因為唔止福建？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f301ca9c5b3cce6bcc647ec0b46ca33a5abc0d","tid":1559720,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97ceb538c306dd39a81aeb8b98b21c446e3103a8","tid":1559720,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:34:42.000Z","msg":"因為唔止福建？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm